r tag-state-power tag-central-planning"><header><p class="tag"><a href="https://reason.com/tag/coronavirus/">Coronavirus</a></p><h1 class="entry-title">People, Not Politicians, Will Decide When the Coronavirus Shutdown Ends</h1><h2 class="entry-subtitle">It's not the politicians who have the power to reopen America, or at least the parts that are now closed. It's individuals, families, businesses, and religious congregations.</h2><p class="meta"> <span class="byline author vcard"> <a href="https://reason.com/people/ira-stoll/" title="Posts by Ira Stoll" class="author url fn" rel="author">Ira Stoll</a> </span> <span class="pipe">|</span> <time class="updated" datetime="2020-04-15T07:00:06-04:00">4.15.2020 7:00 AM</time></p><div class="rcom-social-tools"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2Fpeople-not-politicians-will-decide-when-the-coronavirus-shutdown-ends%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--facebook" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Facebook" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2Fpeople-not-politicians-will-decide-when-the-coronavirus-shutdown-ends%2F&text=It%27s+not+the+politicians+who+have+the+power+to+reopen+America%2C+or+at+least+the+parts+that+are+now+closed.+It%27s+individuals%2C+families%2C+businesses%2C+and+religious+congregations.&via=reason" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--twitter" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Twitter" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a><a href="https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2Fpeople-not-politicians-will-decide-when-the-coronavirus-shutdown-ends%2F&title=It%27s+not+the+politicians+wh