ieing or waiting =for someone to nanny us?<br /> GROW UP. Take responsibility for your OWN life. Stop trying to usurp responsibiilty for everyonie else&#039;s life.</p></div><div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-login" href="https://reason.com/wp-login.php?redirect_to=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2Fpeople-not-politicians-will-decide-when-the-coronavirus-shutdown-ends%2F">Log in to Reply <i class="fas fa-reply"></i></a></div></div></li><li class="comment byuser even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-8212406" data-sort-time="1587028726"><div id="div-comment-8212406" class="comment-body"><div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><div class="comment-author vcard"> <cite class="fn"><strong>Granite</strong></cite></div> <a href="https://reason.com/2020/04/15/people-not-politicians-will-decide-when-the-coronavirus-shutdown-ends/#comment-8212406">April.16.2020 at 5:18 am </a></div><div class="comment-content"><p>The goddamn churches dont even pay taxes &#8211; they can be opened last. Dead last. Weve got much bigger fish to fry than fucking 2000 years ago goat herder worshippers. Its fucking pathetic.</p></div><div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-login" href="https://reason.com/wp-login.php?redirect_to=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2Fpeople-not-politicians-will-decide-when-the-coronavirus-shutdown-ends%2F">Log in to Reply <i class="fas fa-reply"></i></a></div></div></li><li class="comment byuser odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-8212480" data-sort-time="1587038430"><div id="div-comment-8212480" class="comment-body"><div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><div class="comment-author vcard"> <cite class="fn"><strong>Number 2</strong></cite></div> <a href="https://reason.com/2020/04/15/people-not-politicians-will-decide-when-the-coronavirus-shutdown-ends/#comment-8212480">April.16.2020 at 8:00 am </a></div><div class="comment-content"><p>Did anyone catch this comment from NJ Gov. Phil Murphy:</p